     is sufficient. For handlers, export only the public handle* functions.
     Effort: ~15 minutes. One line per module.

  B) -Wunused-imports (28 warnings)
     Fix: Delete the unused import lines.
     Effort: ~20 minutes. Straightforward line deletions.

  C) -Wderiving-defaults (12 warnings, all in Types.hs)
     Fix: Change `deriving (Show, Eq, ...)` to `deriving (Show, Eq, ...) via any class`.
     Actually: Since these use `DeriveAnyClass`, need `deriving stock (Show, Eq, ...)` 
     or add `default ()` in deriving strategy.
     Effort: ~5 minutes. All in one file.

  D) -Worphans (4 warnings, all in Store.hs)
     Fix: Move orphan instances to Types.hs where BucketName/ObjectKey are defined,
     or add `newtype` wrappers in Store.hs.
     Effort: ~10 minutes. Involves moving code between files.

